    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/891adb51559735151d24df25442d5f6b.poster.avif?t=1727971603\" width=600 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/891adb51559735151d24df25442d5f6b.webm?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/891adb51559735151d24df25442d5f6b.mp4?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>悉心经营小小的一块地方，为音乐节不断增加现金流，积攒名气，吸引观众、乐队和赞助厂商，打造音乐盛会，缔造音乐节帝国。如果觉得任务太过艰巨，也可以进入有趣的沙盒模拟模式，举办你梦寐以求的音乐节活动！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/d99521dc940137fb7369733b27ad2db0.poster.avif?t=1727971603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/d99521dc940137fb7369733b27ad2db0.webm?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/d99521dc940137fb7369733b27ad2db0.mp4?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/af238d571b497a0236e5a5ed8456afbb.poster.avif?t=1727971603\" width=600 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/af238d571b497a0236e5a5ed8456afbb.webm?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/af238d571b497a0236e5a5ed8456afbb.mp4?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>充分利用你的谈判能力，依靠你的音乐品味，走进民谣、摇滚和铁克诺之类的圈子，物色各种类型的优秀组合。许多乐队都希望得到特殊优待，一旦事情不合他们的心意就有可能和你不欢而散。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/ac562f219c2e6a2605466e4d2f50f5fe.poster.avif?t=1727971603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/ac562f219c2e6a2605466e4d2f50f5fe.webm?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/ac562f219c2e6a2605466e4d2f50f5fe.mp4?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/1c72ed5e69a932be41af0a9227bf2862.poster.avif?t=1727971603\" width=600 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/1c72ed5e69a932be41af0a9227bf2862.webm?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/1c72ed5e69a932be41af0a9227bf2862.mp4?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>布设帐篷、贵宾区、舞台、洗手间、活动装饰以及其他项目，充分发挥场地布局的作用，为游客带去更多欢乐与幸福！务必记得灵活设置栏杆，分隔人流量，防止观众上台，否则现场将一片混乱。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/e5412cbca2f972e8da4cd5a66cc7ba28.poster.avif?t=1727971603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/e5412cbca2f972e8da4cd5a66cc7ba28.webm?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/e5412cbca2f972e8da4cd5a66cc7ba28.mp4?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/e6357a0d79e69036678dcbf629f89b5b.poster.avif?t=1727971603\" width=600 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/e6357a0d79e69036678dcbf629f89b5b.webm?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/e6357a0d79e69036678dcbf629f89b5b.mp4?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>吸引银行、唱片公司和饮料公司为你的活动赞助，不过千万注意：如果你不能满足他们的条件，后果将非常严重！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/2c4edda249cbede8ffaa7d81da8484cd.poster.avif?t=1727971603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/2c4edda249cbede8ffaa7d81da8484cd.webm?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/2c4edda249cbede8ffaa7d81da8484cd.mp4?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/92f1cc93c55dab70f6284a8290aece35.poster.avif?t=1727971603\" width=600 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/92f1cc93c55dab70f6284a8290aece35.webm?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/92f1cc93c55dab70f6284a8290aece35.mp4?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>有的观众有了帐篷就很开心，高档VIP观众的要求则会高出许多，你的音乐节会面向哪一类顾客？时刻关注观众的满意程度，不满意的观众很有可能在网上发文吐槽！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/0c8c0fc9086ff411eced57b41e97b3c0.poster.avif?t=1727971603\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/0c8c0fc9086ff411eced57b41e97b3c0.webm?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1326270/extras/0c8c0fc9086ff411eced57b41e97b3c0.mp4?t=1727971603\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
